    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Excerpts of parts of a literary composition, as into another book or writing; use also for statements of market price of one or more securities.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
